Recruiters hand out tote bags filled with branded notebooks and pens as career center staff log attendance metrics on laptops. A post-event survey link flashes on the monitors by the exit, and camera crews from the university media team capture interviews. Meanwhile, career counselors remind attendees to maintain eye contact.
